# TikTok Creator Rewards vs Creativity Program

TikTok has updated its monetization programs several times.

Many creators still wonder about the difference between the Creator Rewards Program and the older Creativity Program.

## What Was The Creativity Program?

The Creativity Program was introduced to encourage longer content.

Creators could earn revenue from eligible videos.

## What Is Creator Rewards?

Creator Rewards is the newer version.

It focuses on:

* Original content
* Viewer engagement
* Watch time
* Audience retention

## Key Differences

| Feature           | Creativity Program | Creator Rewards |
| ----------------- | ------------------ | --------------- |
| Monetization      | Yes                | Yes             |
| Long-form Focus   | Yes                | Yes             |
| Updated Algorithm | No                 | Yes             |
| Current Program   | No                 | Yes             |

## Final Thoughts

Creator Rewards is now the primary TikTok monetization system and offers better opportunities for active creators.
